data.description: Welcome to the highly desirable Hearthstone community and this dreamy home just steps from the community park and playground!  Three bedrooms, three baths, two-car garage with the builder's option which extended the garage four feet for lots of extra space. Have a large vehicle? It'll probably fit as the garage is huge! Don't like the higher current interest rates? Seller offering 5.75% interest rate on purchase loans with seller's preferred lender. Assumable VA loan at 2.5%   It has beautiful gleaming floors, a gorgeous modern kitchen with high-end stainless steel appliances  and custom paint and window treatments throughout the home. The house is built over a crawl space on concrete slab that provides great storage space. Don't miss the cool bonus kids playroom. Open layout on the main level flows seamlessly from living to kitchen, to dining and phenomenal backyard. The back yard includes another bonus: a wonderful additional composite (Trex type material, but better) deck adjacent to the concrete patio with a superb gazebo which is an excellent shady spot in the warm summer afternoons to relax, have a bite of food, or entertain with friends and neighbors. East-facing yard in Colorado means in the summertime the warm evening sun is shielded by the house shade, but in the winter it's still enjoyable as sun warms you up with your favorite hot beverage in the morning. A gorgeous new neighborhood close to all the amenities you'd hope for including three parks, trails and a dog park a block away from your new home that even includes a dog agility course. Enjoy living central to all the amenities you could wish for with endless dining and shopping options just a few mins away. New Spano dog park is 10 min walk. Super close to schools and hospitals. Top Golf and Costco 5 mins away. This area is hot and booming! Backs to greenbelt!
